text: Kurt Innes (born 4 February 1971) is a Canadian former cyclist. He competed in the track time trial at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Canada Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Deloraine, Manitoba Category:Sportspeople from Manitoba
